{"tid":34261,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[歌詞分享] 世上只有","createTime":"2016-12-11T11:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T16:45:47.000Z","uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1215ec3cd9704f18806410fb812c965e970f21f6","tid":34261,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"作詞：黃偉文&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n望著你講 也許更易 濃於水的給我用<br />\n從我降世 幾多種 愛與愛 不休止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n也未及這支柱 能完全欠奉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nYou make me cry make me smile<br />\nMake me feel that love is true<br />\n謝謝你的關顧 與及無償的愛護<br />\n年月漫漫 多艱苦 你也永遠優先拋低我不顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯恐我立下私心 最貼身辜負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOh I love you<br />\n<br />\nWyman D 詞真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2be086eff0ada3758f2e9b9205373bf2b224f3b","tid":34261,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e94c5461c0cf006226e3225f58fee8cc7dbcbad","tid":34261,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎果幾個煩閪唔會入黎呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74eb4f686127c4675f92a7f7dd6ec67fb2653d4d","tid":34261,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"4連了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b3276ccab2a604d57bc3a7899f6f2458838ea5","tid":34261,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep